data.description: Seller is open to buyers assuming his FHA loan at a 5.125 interest rate with $45,000 down. Welcome Home! With open living spaces and vaulted ceilings, the layout of this move-in ready home will not disappoint. The well-appointed kitchen, facing the back yard, is an ideal space for cooking and entertaining. The spacious master bedroom boasts a walk-in closet and a master bath with dual sinks. Down the hall, you will find two comfy bedrooms and a full classic bathroom. The two-car garage has plenty of space for storage and parking while the fenced backyard is where you will enjoy relaxing throughout the seasons. Schedule a showing today with your agent, or call 406-839-6428.
